title: Trump and Sanders Lead in New Hampshire
text:
0 Comment 
A new Gravis Marketing poll in New Hampshire finds Donald Trump leading with 32%, followed by Ben Carson at 13%, John Kasich at 10%, Marco Rubio at 8%, Carly Fiorina at 8% and Jeb Bush at 7%. 
On the Democratic side, Bernie Sanders leads with 33%, followed by Hillary Clinton at 30% and Joe Biden at 11%.
